#CircuitBreakerSg Day 37! Tonight’s simple dinner. Pan Seared Golden Pomfret Steamed in Premium Rice Wine. Recipe adapted from the @wricewine website! Light and nourishing. 😋

W Rice Wine is handcrafted in Singapore. All natural and pure with no added sugar or preservatives and gluten-free. Available at www.wricewine.com/shop!
